These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: raspberry, banana, avocado, pear, cabbage, cauliflower, pomegranate
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating banana##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating pear##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
4. the person eating cabbage is between the person eating raspberry and the person eating avocado##2
5. the person eating pear is between the person eating banana and the person eating raspberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Food   | pomegranate | avocado | cabbage | raspberry | pear | banana | cauliflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different pets are kept: fish, dog, turtle, cat, frog, chinchilla, hamster
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the fish##2
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
6. the owner of the turtle is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Pet   | chinchilla | hamster | fish | turtle | cat | dog | frog |

