.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-10::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: may, october, april, march, june, january, september
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in march##2
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in september##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |   4    |   5    |      6       |     7     |
| Birthday   | january | may | april | september | june | march | october |

