2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
3. the prince-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the prince-smoker is between the baccarat-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##2
6. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
7. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3  |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Cigar   | dunhill | prince | baccarat | vegafina | blend | oliveros | davidoff |

